headline: Best Stock to Buy Right Now: Realty Income vs. W.P. Carey
summary: Realty Income is the largest net lease REIT, with W.P. Carey coming in at No. 2.  Realty Income is focused on retail assets, with W.P. Carey focused on industrial assets.  Realty Income and W.P. Carey both have attractive yields, but their dividend histories are massively different.
